section.form-section
  img.form-section__image(src="assets/images/form-section.jpg" alt="Image" loading="lazy")
  .site-container.form-section__container
    .form-section__block
      h2.form-section__heading
        | Связаться
        | с нами
      form.form-section__form.form
        .form__group
          label.form__control-wrapper
            input.form__control(type="text" name="name" placeholder="Ваше имя")
          label.form__control-wrapper
            input.form__control(type="text" name="company" placeholder="Компания")
          label.form__control-wrapper
            input.form__control(type="text" name="phone" placeholder="Телефон")
          label.form__control-wrapper
            input.form__control(type="text" name="email" placeholder="Email")
        .form__footer
          +button('отправить').form__submit
          p.form__descr
            | Отправляя данную форму вы соглашаетесь
            | #[a(href="./") с политикой обработки данных]
